        <span style="font-weight:700">5.Prototyping, Evaluation and Iteration</span><br>
        For the survey page, two different layouts, one with radio buttons and the other with sliders are developed. A simple A/B test is conducted with three participation to test for optimization.
        From the A/B tests it is learned that the layout with sliders has significant difference in ease of use and the time taken to complete the survey.
      img(style="width:70%;",src="/assets/img/hp_gallery_tn/usabilitytest.png")
      p.
        Based on these results, Layout B (sliders) was used in the final survey application.
